<i>noun</i>: 발열 [바렬], 난방 [난방], 가열 [가열] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>발열 [바렬]</dt><br>
<dd>1. heating; exothermicity</dd><br>
<dd>열이 남. 또는 열을 냄.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of being heated, or the act of generating heat.</dd><br>
<dd>2. fever; febrility</dd><br>
<dd>체온이 높아짐. 또는 그런 증상.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which one's temperature becomes high or such a symptom.</dd><br>
<dt>난방 [난방]</dt><br>
<dd>heating</dd><br>
<dd>건물 안이나 방 안의 온도를 높여 따뜻하게 하는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>Warming the air in a room or building by raising the temperature.</dd><br>
<dt>가열 [가열]</dt><br>
<dd>1. heating</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 물질에 뜨거운 열을 가함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of applying heat to a substance.</dd><br>
<dd>2. being heated</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일이나 사건에 대하여 관심이 집중되고 분위기가 흥분됨.</dd><br>
<dd>Focused interest and excitement about an event or incident.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>